longBusinessSummary: ZENKOKU HOSHO Co.,Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the credit guarantee business in Japan. It is also involved in the non-life insurance agency and credit check operations; and the provision of contracting and clerical services. In addition, the company engages in the debt collection business, as well as acts as an agent. ZENKOKU HOSHO Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
